                            <comment id="88533" author="adilger" created="Tue, 8 Jul 2014 21:14:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This needs to be changed in a few places in the Lustre code:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;contrib/lbuild/lbuild:    Do not try to download a kernel from downloads.lustre.org
contrib/lbuild/lbuild:            local location=&quot;http://downloads.lustre.org/public/kernels/$target/old&quot;
contrib/lbuild/lbuild:    local location=&quot;https://www.openfabrics.org/downloads/OFED/ofed-${OFED_BASE_VERSION}/&quot;
contrib/lbuild/lbuild:        location=&quot;http://www.openfabrics.org/downloads/OFED/ofed-${Mmv}/&quot;
contrib/lbuild/lbuild:        location=&quot;http://www.openfabrics.org/downloads/OFED/ofed-${Mmv}-daily/&quot;
lustre/BUILDING:kernel and utilities from http://downloads.lustre.org/
lustre/doc/lustre.7:http://downloads.whamcloud.com/
lustre/utils/mount_utils_ldiskfs.c:             &quot;http://downloads.whamcloud.com/public/e2fsprogs/latest/\n&quot;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
